Package cz.vse.java.connections.utils.management

Class ClientServiceManagement

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.vse.java.connections.utils.management.AConnectionManager
      • cz.vse.java.connections.utils.management.ClientServiceManagement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IObserver, ISubject, java.lang.Runnable
    public class ClientServiceManagement
extends AConnectionManager
implements ISubject, IObserver, java.lang.Runnable

    The class of ClientServiceManagement is used to abstractly define the type of the instances.

    These instances are responsible for managing connection with service from client.

    Written for project "Connections2".

    06. 04. 2020 .vse.java.connections.utils.management
